~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Author: Chris Arriola
Date:   Dec. 9, 2010
Description: A squarelotron game. It will ask you whether to use a 4x4 or a
    5x5 squarelotron, then print out the initial squarelotron. Thent the 
    program will let you tell it which flips to perform and it will print out
    the new squarelotron after each flip. This is based on Dr. Dave Matuszek's
    CIT591 class - www.cis.upenn.edu/~matuszek/
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
